overview: Federico Hradek and Delilah Jane Dunn present: "BEETLEJUICE: The Online Musical!"-- a project for the fans, by the fans! This fan-made project tells the story of Lydia Deetz, a young girl who mourns her mother's death, and is obsessed with all things strange and unusual. However, when she meets the ghost with the most (you know his name!) her world suddenly flips upside down. With twists, turns, comedy, puppets, CGI, and sheer laughter from the hereafter-- what could go wrong?
title: Beetlejuice: The Online Musical
